	 	acgeneral.m4 autoconf.m4f
		Added new options: --varprefix=
	  --mmdf-debug=[0,1,2]    enable more logging information
	  --mmdf-dlog             enable debug-option of dial packages
	  --mmdf-dbglog           enable debug-option of dial packages
	  --mmdf-nodomlit         toggle define NODOMLIT
	  --mmdf-leftdots         toggle define LEFTDOTS
	  --mmdf-statsort         toggle define STATSORT
	  --mmdf-citation         toggle define CITATION
	  --mmdf-prefix=DIR       default home of mmdf in DIR [PREFIX/mmdf]
	       Fixed directory substitution

	* autoconf/autoconf.m4f, autoconf/acgeneral.m4:
	Added acgeneral.m4 and autoconf.m4f to head-branch

